                    <h4>Standard (automatic tracking)</h4>
                    <div class="code-block">
                        <code>@@inherits ComponentBase</code>
                    </div>
                    <p>✓ Component tree<br />✓ Basic render tracking<br />✓ Timeline events</p>
                </div>

                <div class="code-comparison enhanced">
